| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1009 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b136e9b2-1c15-5430-9182-2d9d3f9ba0ef"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
